@context: DemoQA Gauntlet - Comprehensive UI Elements Test. Covers forms, checkbox trees, radio buttons, dynamic web tables, multi-click buttons, select menus, and date pickers.
@blueprint: full_ui_element_suite

# 🐾 DEMOQA GAUNTLET: The Full Elements Challenge
# Масштабна перевірка всіх базових компонентів веб-інтерфейсу.

# ── 1. Forms: Текстові поля та сабміт ────────────────────────────────
1. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/text-box
2. Fill 'Full Name' field with 'Ghost Manul'
3. Fill 'Email' field with 'ghost@manul.ai'
4. Fill 'Current Address' field with '42 Shadow Lane'
5. Fill 'Permanent Address' field with '7 Phantom Street'
6. Click the 'Submit' button
7. VERIFY that 'Ghost Manul' and 'ghost@manul.ai' are present.

8. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/checkbox
9. Click the expand arrow button
10. Click the checkbox for 'Home'
11. WAIT 2
12. VERIFY that 'You have selected' is present.

13. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/radio-button
14. Click the radio button for 'Impressive'
15. VERIFY that 'Impressive' is present.

16. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/webtables
17. EXTRACT the Salary of 'Alden' into {alden_salary}
18. VERIFY that '2000' is present.

19. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/buttons
20. DOUBLE CLICK the 'Double Click Me' button
21. VERIFY that 'You have done a double click' is present.
22. Click the 'Click Me' button
23. VERIFY that 'You have done a dynamic click' is present.

24. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/select-menu
25. Select 'Purple' from the 'Select Value' dropdown
26. VERIFY that 'Purple' is present.

27. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/date-picker
28. Fill 'Date Of Birth' field with '01/15/1990'
29. VERIFY that '01/15/1990' is present.

30. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/slider
31. VERIFY that 'Slider' is present.

32. NAVIGATE to https://demoqa.com/links
33. Click on the 'Home' link

34. DONE.